Dataflow_SetOperation_AND: Select elements that are selected in both incoming selections (Bitwise AND)
Dataflow_SetOperation_OR: Select elements that are selected in either incoming selections (Bitwise OR)
Dataflow_SetOperation_XOR: Select elements that are selected in exactly one incoming selection (Bitwise XOR)
Dataflow_SetOperation_Subtract: Select elements that are selected in only the first of the incoming selections (Bitwise A AND (NOT B))
